  "text": "Methods. Now let us compare our scheme with the basic probabilistic scheme [CITATION_1] , the qcomposite scheme [CITATION_2] ], and the random subset assignment scheme [CITATION_3] . As discussed earlier, our proposed scheme has a high probability to establish direct keys between neighbor sensor nodes given reasonable capacity density ratio γ and maximum deployment errors. At the same time, our scheme does not put any direct limitation on the network size.",
